                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341205-214-offence-1 t18341205-cd-13"></join>27th of November</rs>, 26 yards of rope, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18341205-name-167" type="victimName">
